---
title: Beef and Cheesy Mash Pie with Green Beans
description: This Beef and Cheesy Mash Pie is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R03_W11_UK_R1656-28_Main_swap_low-40996687.jpg
